name: Rebel Reinforcements
Lore: 'Rebels rely on hidden ''cells'' of undercover operatives. Striking from hidden bases, troops or starfighters can arrive in a battle zone at any time.',
Text: 'If Opponent outnumbers you in total characters and starships on table, use 1 Force to draw destiny. That number of Rebel Troopers and/or Y-Wings, may be retrieved from Lost Pile.',
